videos.description: Norman Powell tries to score, but Ben Simmons chases him down and blocks the shot so hard it sends Powell to the floor.

videos.headline: Simmons chases down Powell to emphatically block his shot

videos.description: Aron Baynes loses the ball and the 76ers try to recover to no avail, leading to Baynes picking it back up for a dunk.
